title: Fond|Data by Finalytica [In Progress]
description: Currently working on a project with the aim of displaying quarterly reported data for Swedish Mutual funds (open data). It's a fullstack project where the data is stored in a MySQL database, a REST-API created in node.js, frontend using TypeScript, React as framework and VITE as building tool.

title: FINALYTICA [In Progress]
description: Currently solely an iOS app providing financial data for publicly listed companies on the NSYE and NASDAQ. Includes historical financial data (+10 years), SEC fillings, financial reports, insider trading, etc.

title: SKYLTEN [REMOVED]
description: Sweden's first image classifier for parking signs. The app was integrated with a custom trained classifier programmed in Python, exported as a CoreML file, providing the user with sophisticated predictions (classification) of the taken image, also returning a result distribution (likelihoods).
